Package neureka.calculus

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CallExecutor  
    Function
    Besides the Tsr class, which is the core class of Neureka, this interface and its implementations represents the second most important feature of this library.
    Function.CallOptions  
    RecursiveExecutor
    Resembles a grouped execution according to arity an implementation specific arity.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cache
    This class is part of a given OperationContext instance responsible for caching Function references based on their String representation generated by Object.toString() as well as caching of results for active functions.
    CalcUtil
    This is a utility class which helps with orchestrating the execution of classical operations from calculus like the operators '*', '-', '+', '/', as well as linear operations like matrix multiplication, broadcasting and convolution.
